race.description: Grafton Gas & Plumbing Country Boosted Hcp
race.comment: GAMING (4) has gone to a new level this campaign and is chasing his third-straight win today. Allowed to take control early in the small field when a game winner with the 57.5kg over 1310m at Lismore. Goes just as well over this trip and gets map favours with the claim. Hard to stop in this rich vein of form. LADY ALABAMA (8) continued to race well since stretching out in trip. Strong through the line when an unlucky second over 1310m at Lismore. Can sit off them from the draw and pounce late. NEVER ISLAND (3) in need of the run first-up when a battling seventh over 1310m at Lismore. Will appreciate the claim and close off strongly. WILDERNESS STAR (10) tough mare who gets a better set-up at this level. Will push forward from the draw and has a good record here.
